Package: resourcetracker
Type: Package
Title: Nowcasting Australian Mining Export Volumes from AIS Shipping Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("David", "Stephan", email = "david.stephan@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    Per-commodity quarterly physical-tonnage nowcasts of Australian iron
    ore and coal exports. Bridge regressions per commodity using IMF
    PortWatch AIS daily tonnage as the high-frequency RHS indicator and
    DISR Resources and Energy Quarterly Table 16 as the tonnage target.
